Theme: Lightash v1.1 for glFusion v1.3.0
Theme by: Walter Rowe - TravelPhotographers.net
Last updated: July 2012
========================================
Lightash is built from glFusion's nouveau theme. It is a fixed & fluid width, light grey (ash) color scheme.

It includes customizations to the overall look and feel of nouveau, and it includes customizations to templates
for the following glFusion plugins in {site_url}/layout/lightash/plugins:

- filemgmt
- forum
- links
- mediagallery
- profile

For complete documentation on the nouveau theme visit: http://www.glfusion.org/wiki/doku.php?id=glfusion:nouveau
and see the README file included with the nouveau theme.
